FORMER Radio One DJ Chris Denning was jailed for four and a half years yesterday by a Czech court for paedophile acts with boys as young as 13.

Denning, 58, from Bracknell, Berkshire, who admitted having been an occasional child prostitute himself, was convicted on seven charges. He denied having sexual acts with a series of boys while in Prague on business.


